HEADWORD: Illegible
<hw>Il*leg"i*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Incapable of
being read; not legible; <as>as, <ex>illegible</ex> handwriting; an
<ex>illegible</ex> inscription.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Il*leg"i*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Il*leg"i*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

